The paper discusses learning on Grassmann manifold in computer vision tasks, which is a common topic in the computer vision community (cs.CV). The proposed method is an unsupervised dimensionality reduction algorithm, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the performance of the proposed method on classification and clustering tasks, which are common topics in multimedia (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT).
